{
  "stem": "1568.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The necessary-- it is going back a long time, and it is something that I have really never talked about, my experience.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was people-- it is amazing, we mingle between mostly Holocaust survivors, and any subjects we talk-- politics to anything-- we end up talking about the Holocaust.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I never, for whatever reason-- I have four kids and they knew I'm a survivor, and I never told them the story.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So because of me not being repetitious throughout this year, I guess my memory has elapsed in certain things, especially dates and times.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Anyway, in Flossenburg, we were until about April, middle of April.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And all the time you were in Flossenburg they had you working in this rock quarry breaking these rocks.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's where I was.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Eight, 10 hours sitting in cold or sun and breaking those-- those rocks.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Again, I saw people being killed around me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I saw people being beaten around me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "If I had an angel looking over me or whatever, I personally was not exposed as individually, but the tragedies and atrocities I saw around me being done.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not really.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I guess of course, I must have talked to people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There must have been people, but for some reason or other-- maybe because I was so puny, and maybe because I kind of sheltered in [? there ?], I did not seek people and people somehow did not seek me out.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I cannot specifically say that I had I mean, close friends that I can recall as-- as individuals.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Of course, all the kids that I was in Birkenau somehow disappeared.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know, when we went to Flossenburg I just-- because I think when they send out from Auschwitz, they send them to different camps.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
